<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.4.6">
<l>takavuṭai yavaṉē yeṉṉumpiṉṉu</l>
<l>mikavirum pumpirā ṉeṉṉumeṉat</l>
<l>takavuyirk kamutē yeṉṉumuḷḷa</l>
<l>mukavu rukiniṉ ṟuḷḷuḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“O you who possess fitness”, she says, [then] again,</l>
<l>“lord who is much desired”, she says, “ambrosia</l>
<l>that is befitting for my life”, she says, constantly</l>
<l>melting inside while [her] heart is rejoicing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
